s><s>Cells are non-motile, ovoid to rod-shaped.</s><s>Spores and flagella are not found.</s><s>Mesophilic.</s><s>Aerobic.</s><s>The major respiratory quinone is MK-12.</s><s>The main fatty acids are C<sub>16 : 0</sub>, C<sub>16 : 1</sub>, C<sub>14 : 0</sub> and C<sub>15 : 0</sub>.</s><s>The G+C content of genomic DNA of the type species is 62.4 %.</s><s>The type species is <em>Armatimonas rosea</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>